Recipe: #008 - Pale Ale Warrior Topaz (23L)
Brewer: 
Asst Brewer: 
Style: American Pale Ale
TYPE: All Grain
Taste: (30.0) 2016-04-11 - Sample from primary. Well balanced. Clean bitterness. Enough malt in the back to counter the hops. Malt not very complex. Recommend maybe adding a bit of crystal to give it a bit of caramel or biscuit malt. Or maybe use marris otter for the base malt, or perhaps 50/50 mixture?

